R code and data to generate the analysis in:

Cardoso, P., Fukushima, C.S. & Mammola, S. (subm.) Quantifying the international collaboration of researchers and research institutions.

The repository contains:

- A folder "Data" contain all data. Data can be generated from input data (authors.rds) with the script Data_extraction.R; note that output data are available;

- Output figures, available in the folder "Figure";

- Code Cardoso_et_al_TREE.R allows the user to reproduce figures and analyses.